'From Squeak2.6 of 13 October 1999 [latest update: #1591] on 1 November 1999 at 10:18:24 am'!"Change Set:		FasterAll-arDate:			1 November 1999Author:			Andreas RaabSpeed up gathering all method selectors for smart updates."!!ClassOrganizer methodsFor: 'elvis' stamp: 'ar 11/1/1999 10:15'!allMethodSelectors	"give a list of all method selectors."	| out |	out _ WriteStream on: (Array new: 100).	self categories do:[:c| c ifNotNil:[out nextPutAll: (self listAtCategoryNamed: c)]].	^out contents sort! !